:"Huntingdon, Huntingdonshire, Inglaterra","lifeSummary":"Thomas Leete nasceu aproximadamente 1474, em Ipswich, Suffolk, Inglaterra filho de Thomas Leete e Alse Huntington. Ele casou-se com Maria Slade em 1500, em Inglaterra. Eles tiveram pelo menos 1 filho. Ele faleceu em 9 de julho de 1554, em Oakington, Cambridgeshire, Inglaterra, com 81 anos, e foi sepultado em Oakington, Cambridgeshire, Inglaterra."},"ro":{"about 1474–9 July 1554":"aproximativ 1474–9 iulie 1554","1474–1554":"1474–1554","1508–1564":"1508–1564","1478–1510":"1478–1510","1500–1551":"1500–1551","1444–1495":"1444–1495","–1506":"–1506","9 July 1554":"9 iulie 1554","25 September 1510":"25 septembrie 1510","1495":"1495","1500":"1500","1478":"1478","1444":"1444","1510":"1510","1554":"1554","1564":"1564","3 February 1506":"3 februarie 1506","1474":"1474","1551":"1551","1508":"1508","about 1474":"aproximativ 1474","3 February 1495":"3 februarie 1495","1506":"1506","25 December 1551":"25 decembrie 1551","1549":"1549","Little Eversden, Cambridgeshire, England":"Little Eversden, Cambridgeshire, England","England":"England","Little Eversden, Ipswich, Suffolk, England":"Ipswich, Suffolk, England","Oakington, Cambridgeshire, England":"Oakington, Cambridgeshire, England","Huntington, Huntingtonshire, England":"Huntingdon, Huntingdonshire, England"},"ru":{"about 1474–9 July 1554":"около 1474 г.–9 июля 1554 г.","1474–1554":"1474г.–1554г.","1508–1564":"1508г.–1564г.","1478–1510":"1478г.–1510г.","1500–1551":"1500г.–1551г.","1444–1495":"1444г.–1495г.","–1506":"–1506г.","9 July 1554":"9 июля 1554 г.","25 September 1510":"25 сентября 1510 г.","1495":"1495 г.","1500":"1500 г.","1478":"1478 г.","1444":"1444 г.","1510":"1510 г.","1554":"1554 г.","1564":"1564 г.","3 February 1506":"3 февраля 1506 г.","1474":"1474 г.","1551":"1551 г.","1508":"1508 г.","about 1474":"около 1474 г.","3 February 1495":"3 февраля 1495 г.","1506":"1506 г.","25 December 1551":"25 декабря 1551 г.","1549":"1549 г.","Little Eversden, Cambridgeshire, E